Class SectionDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.tool.section.decorator.SectionDecorator

    public class SectionDecorator
extends Object
implements RowGroupable, Serializable, Comparable
    Decorates a CourseSection for use in the instructor's (and TA's) page views.
